{
  "title": "Warm Spicy Saudi Arabian Chicken Tagine",
  "description": "A savory and flavorful Saudi Arabian dish made with chicken, coconut cream, and spices, perfect for a weeknight dinner. This low-calorie-friendly recipe is cooked in a fondue pot to create a delicious and healthy meal.",
  "cuisine": "Saudi Arabian",
